  m_text: "Trong chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u\n- \u0110\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u
    ta c\u1EA7n ch\xFA \xFD:\n  + <color=red>Lv, m\xE1u hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i, h\u1EC7</color=red>
    pokemon\n  + Fight \u0111\u1EC3 d\xF9ng <color=red>k\u1EF9 n\u0103ng</color=red>\n 
    + Pokemon \u0111\u1EC3 <color=red>chuy\u1EC3n pokemon</color=red> ra tr\u1EADn\n 
    + Item \u0111\u1EC3 <color=red>d\xF9ng v\u1EADt ph\u1EA9m</color=red> h\u1ED3i
    ph\u1EE5c ho\u1EB7c pokeball\n  + Run \u0111\u1EC3 <color=red>tho\xE1t chi\u1EBFn
    \u0111\u1EA5u</color=red>\n\n- Ti\u1EBFp theo l\xE0 \u0111\u1EBFn <color=red>k\u1EF9
    n\u0103ng (moves)</color=red> c\u1EE7a pokemon:\n  + K\u1EF9 n\u0103ng c\xF3
    <color=red>h\u1EC7, power, pp(s\u1ED1 l\u1EA7n s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng)</color=red>\n 
    + m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 k\u1EF9 n\u0103ng c\xF3 th\u1EC3 <color=red>t\u0103ng, gi\u1EA3m
    ch\u1EC9 s\u1ED1</color=red>\n  + m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 k\u1EF9 n\u0103ng c\xF3 th\u1EC3
    g\xE2y <color=red>hi\u1EC7u \u1EE9ng \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t</color=red>: ng\u1EE7,
    tr\xFAng \u0111\u1ED9c, T\xCA Li\u1EC7t,...\n"
