  m_text: "- T\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c v\u1EDBi NPC \u0111\u1EC3: \n  + Xem pokemon
    c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1ED1i th\u1EE7 v\xE0 c\xF3 th\u1EC3 chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u,
    chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c <color=red>kinh nhi\u1EC7m v\xE0 ti\u1EC1n</color=red>\n 
    + NPC shop s\u1EBD b\xE1n nh\u1EEFng <color=red>v\u1EADt ph\u1EA9m h\u1ED3i ph\u1EE5c
    ho\u1EB7c pokeball</color=red>\n  + NPC healer s\u1EBD h\u1ED3i ph\u1EE5c <color=red>HP
    v\xE0 tr\u1EA1ng th\xE1i</color=red> cho to\xE0n b\u1ED9 pokemon c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n\n 
    + NPC gi\u1EEF kho s\u1EBD gi\u1EEF nh\u1EEFng <color=red>pokemon m\xE0 b\u1EA1n
    g\u1EEDi</color=red> v\xE0o  (1 \u0111\u1ED9i h\xECnh ch\u1EC9 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    <color=red><= 6 pokemon</color=red> n\xEAn nh\u1EEFng pokemon kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n
    d\xF9ng ho\u1EB7c th\u1EEBa ra c\xF3 th\u1EC3 g\u1EEDi v\xE0o kho)"
